---
const title = "Bastión Defensa | Continuidad Operativa y SecOps";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Bastión Defensa | Ciberseguridad Profesional en Albacete y España — SecOps y Continuidad Operativa</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Bastión Defensa: servicios de ciberseguridad profesional en Albacete y toda España. Vigilancia 24/7, respuesta ante incidentes, auditoría continua y diagnóstico de resiliencia. Trato directo de experto."/>
  <meta name="keywords" content="ciberseguridad Albacete, seguridad informática España, SOC Albacete, respuesta incidentes ciberseguridad, auditoría seguridad informática, continuidad operativa, SecOps, hardening sistemas, Wazuh, bastión defensa"/>
  <meta name="author" content="Bastión Defensa"/>
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow"/>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.bastiondefensa.com/"/>

  <meta property="og:title" content="Bastión Defensa | Ciberseguridad Profesional en Albacete y España"/>
  <meta property="og:description" content="Monitorizamos infraestructuras críticas y cerramos brechas de seguridad para que tu negocio no se detenga. Trato directo de experto."/>
  <meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.bastiondefensa.com/"/>
  <meta property="og:locale" content="es_ES"/>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ProfessionalService",
    "name": "Bastión Defensa",
    "description": "Servicios de ciberseguridad profesional, SecOps y continuidad operativa en Albacete y toda España.",
    "url": "https://www.bastiondefensa.com",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "addressLocality": "Albacete",
      "addressRegion": "Castilla-La Mancha",
      "addressCountry": "ES"
    },
    "areaServed": [
      {"@type": "City", "name": "Albacete"},
      {"@type": "Country", "name": "España"}
    ],
    "serviceType": ["Ciberseguridad", "SecOps", "Auditoría de Seguridad", "Respuesta ante Incidentes", "Continuidad Operativa"],
    "founder": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Mario"},
    "sameAs": []
  }
  </script>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

    :root {
      --navy: #0f1d3a;
      --navy-mid: #162347;
      --navy-light: #1c2d58;
      --slate: #2a3a5c;
      --sky: #e8eef6;
      --sky-warm: #f4f6fa;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --teal: #0d9488;
      --teal-light: #14b8a6;
      --teal-bg: rgba(13,148,136,.08);
      --teal-border: rgba(13,148,136,.2);
      --amber: #f59e0b;
      --amber-bg: rgba(245,158,11,.1);
      --text-dark: #1a2740;
      --text: #475569;
      --text-light: #94a3b8;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,29,58,.06);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 20px rgba(15,29,58,.08);
      --shadow-lg: 0 8px 40px rgba(15,29,58,.12);
      --font: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
      --radius: 14px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--font);
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    a { color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1140px; margin:0 auto;
      display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
      height: 68px;
    }
    .logo {
      display: flex; align-items:center; gap:.6rem;
      font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--navy);
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--slate) 100%);
      border-radius: 9px;
      display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    }
    .logo-icon svg { width:20px; height:20px; }
    .nav-links { display:flex; gap:2rem; list-style:none; align-items:center; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--text); font-size:.9rem; font-weight:500; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--teal); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--navy) !important;
      color: var(--white) !important;
      padding: .55rem 1.3rem !important;
      border-radius: 9px;
      font-size: .85rem !important;
      font-weight: 600 !important;
      transition: all .25s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--navy-mid) !important; transform:translateY(-1px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }

    .hamburger { display:none; background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; padding:4px; }
    .hamburger svg { stroke: var(--navy); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem;
      background: linear-gradient(170deg, var(--sky-warm) 0%, var(--white) 55%);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content:''; position:absolute; top:-120px; right:-80px;
      width: 500px; height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(13,148,136,.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1140px; margin:0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px; gap: 4rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:.5rem;
      background: var(--teal-bg); border: 1px solid var(--teal-border);
      color: var(--teal); font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 600;
      padding: .4rem 1rem; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      animation: fadeUp .7s ease both;
    }
    .hero-badge svg { width:14px; height:14px; }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem); font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
      animation: fadeUp .7s ease .1s both;
    }
    h1 span { color: var(--teal); }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text); max-width: 500px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem; animation: fadeUp .7s ease .2s both;
    }
    .hero-note {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .82rem; color: var(--text-light);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--teal); padding-left: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem; animation: fadeUp .7s ease .3s both;
    }
    .hero-btns { display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; animation: fadeUp .7s ease .4s both; }

    .trust-card {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      padding: 2rem; animation: fadeUp .7s ease .3s both;
    }
    .trust-card h3 {
      font-size: .75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .trust-item {
      display: flex; align-items:flex-start; gap: 1rem;
      padding: .9rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .trust-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .trust-icon {
      width: 38px; height: 38px; flex-shrink:0;
      background: var(--teal-bg); border-radius: 9px;
      display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      color: var(--teal); font-size: .95rem;
    }
    .trust-item strong { display:block; color: var(--text-dark); font-size:.9rem; font-weight:600; }
    .trust-item span { font-size:.82rem; color:var(--text-light); }

    /* BUTTONS */
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font); font-weight: 700; font-size: .9rem;
      padding: .85rem 1.8rem; border-radius: 10px;
      transition: all .25s; cursor: pointer; border: none;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--teal); color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(13,148,136,.25);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--teal-light); transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(13,148,136,.3);
    }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent; color: var(--navy);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      border-color: var(--teal-border); background: var(--teal-bg); color: var(--teal);
    }

    /* SECTIONS */
    section { padding: 6rem 2rem;  scroll-margin-top: 30px; }
    .container { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label {
      font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: .6rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.3rem); font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: .75rem;
    }
    .section-desc { color: var(--text); max-width: 560px; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

    /* MANIFIESTO */
    .manifiesto { background: var(--sky-warm); }
    .mani-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
    .mani-text p { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size:1.02rem; }
    .stack-row { display: flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.5rem; margin-top:1.5rem; }
    .stack-chip {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 500;
      padding: .35rem .85rem; background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 7px; color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .terminal {
      background: var(--navy); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.8rem;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .8rem; line-height: 2;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .terminal::before {
      content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:40px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    }
    .term-dots { position:relative; z-index:1; display:flex; gap:6px; margin-bottom:1.2rem; }
    .term-dots i { width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:50%; display:block; }
    .term-dots i:nth-child(1){ background:#ff5f57; }
    .term-dots i:nth-child(2){ background:#febc2e; }
    .term-dots i:nth-child(3){ background:#28c840; }
    .tg { color: var(--teal-light); }
    .tw { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); }

    /* SERVICIOS */
    .svc-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .svc-card {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem;
      transition: all .3s; position: relative;
    }
    .svc-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal-border); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .svc-num { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .7rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .svc-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
    }
    .svc-icon.shield { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(13,148,136,.12), rgba(13,148,136,.04)); color: var(--teal); }
    .svc-icon.lock { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15,29,58,.1), rgba(15,29,58,.03)); color: var(--navy); }
    .svc-icon.chart { background: var(--amber-bg); color: var(--amber); }
    .svc-card h3 { font-size: 1.08rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: .7rem; }
    .svc-card p { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65; }
    .svc-tag {
      display: inline-block; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--teal); background: var(--teal-bg);
      padding: .2rem .65rem; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 1.1rem;
    }

    /* MARIO */
    .mario-section { background: var(--navy); color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }
    .mario-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: 3.5rem; align-items: center; }
    .mario-avatar {
      width: 150px; height: 150px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(13,148,136,.25), rgba(13,148,136,.05));
      border: 2px solid rgba(13,148,136,.3); border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--teal-light);
    }
    .mario-section .section-label { color: var(--teal-light); }
    .mario-section h2 { color: var(--white); }
    .mario-role { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .82rem; color: var(--teal-light); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .mario-section p { margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .pills { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .pill { display: flex; align-items:center; gap:.45rem; font-size: .82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); }
    .pill-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; background: var(--teal-light); border-radius: 50%; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section { background: var(--sky-warm); text-align:center; }
    .cta-box {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px; padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .cta-box h2 { margin-bottom: .6rem; }
    .cta-box > p { color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-btns { display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }

    .local-section { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .local-section p { color: var(--text-light); font-size: .92rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      display: flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
      max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
    }
    footer p { font-size:.8rem; color:var(--text-light); }
    .footer-logo { font-weight:800; color:var(--navy); font-size:.95rem; }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(22px); }
      to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
    }
    .fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity .55s ease, transform .55s ease; }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .trust-card { max-width: 420px; }
      .svc-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; max-width:480px; }
      .mani-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .mario-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; text-align:center; justify-items:center; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .nav-links { display:none; }
      .hamburger { display:block; }
      .nav-links.open {
        display:flex; flex-direction:column;
        position:absolute; top:68px; left:0; right:0;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.97); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); gap: 1rem;
      }
      section { padding: 4rem 1.2rem; }
      .hero { padding: 8rem 1.2rem 4rem; }
      .cta-box { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
      footer { flex-direction:column; text-align:center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="#" class="logo">
      <div class="logo-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      Bastión Defensa
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <li><a href="#manifiesto">Manifiesto</a></li>
      <li><a href="#servicios">Servicios</a></li>
      <li><a href="#mario">Quién soy</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contacto" class="nav-cta">Contactar</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="hamburger" onclick="document.getElementById('navLinks').classList.toggle('open')" aria-label="Menú">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/></svg>
    </button>
  </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero" id="inicio">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        Ciberseguridad en Albacete y toda España
      </div>
      <h1>Si hoy sufres un ciberataque, <span>¿podrá tu negocio abrir mañana?</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Porque un antivirus ya no es suficiente. Blindamos tu infraestructura para que tu empresa nunca deje de facturar.</p>
      <p class="hero-note">Sin comerciales ni niveles de soporte. <b>Habla directamente con el ingeniero</b> que diseña y ejecuta tu defensa.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary">
          Solicitar diagnóstico gratuito
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#servicios" class="btn btn-outline">Ver servicios</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-card">
      <h3>Por qué confiar en Bastión</h3>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <div class="trust-icon">🔍</div>
        <div><strong>Transparencia total</strong><span>Sin letra pequeña ni costes ocultos.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <div class="trust-icon">⚡</div>
        <div><strong>Vigilancia 24/7</strong><span>Detección continua de amenazas, incluso de madrugada.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <div class="trust-icon">🏢</div>
        <div><strong>Enfoque PYME</strong><span>Soluciones prácticas adaptadas a tu tamaño real.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <div class="trust-icon">📋</div>
        <div><strong>Soberanía de datos</strong><span>Tu información es tuya y siempre lo será. Sin ataduras.</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="manifiesto" id="manifiesto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mani-grid">
      <div class="mani-text fade-in">
        <p class="section-label">Nuestro manifiesto</p>
        <h2>Seguridad transparente. Sin opacidad de fabricante.</h2>
        <p>Implementamos sistemas de defensa basados en <strong>estándares abiertos</strong>. Tu seguridad no depende de pagar licencias abusivas ni de quedar atrapado en nubes cerradas.</p>
        <p>El resultado: una protección auditable donde la propiedad de los registros y la inteligencia de defensa siempre te pertenecen.</p>
        <div class="stack-row">
          <span class="stack-chip">Wazuh</span>
          <span class="stack-chip">TheHive</span>
          <span class="stack-chip">MITRE ATT&CK</span>
          <span class="stack-chip">CIS Benchmarks</span>
          <span class="stack-chip">ENS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal fade-in">
        <div class="term-dots"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
        <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
          <span style="opacity:.4">// estado de tu infraestructura</span><br/>
          <span class="tg">→</span> <span class="tw">wazuh-agent</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#34d399">● activo</span><br/>
          <span class="tg">→</span> <span class="tw">thehive-core</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#34d399">● activo</span><br/>
          <span class="tg">→</span> <span class="tw">firewall-rules</span> &nbsp;<span style="color:#34d399">● sincronizado</span><br/>
          <span class="tg">→</span> <span class="tw">vuln-scan</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#fbbf24">● ejecutando…</span><br/>
          <span class="tg">→</span> <span class="tw">data-ownership</span> &nbsp;<span style="color:#34d399">● cliente</span><br/>
          <br/>
          <span style="opacity:.4">// sin cajas negras. sin dependencia.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="servicios">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label fade-in">Servicios</p>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Plan Integral de Continuidad Operativa</h2>
    <p class="section-desc fade-in">Proteger, endurecer y recuperar. Tu negocio bajo control <b>desde 450€/mes.</b></p>
    <div class="svc-grid">
      <article class="svc-card fade-in">
        <p class="svc-num">01</p>
        <div class="svc-icon shield">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Vigilancia y Respuesta Activa</h3>
        <p>Detección de intrusiones y respuesta técnica ante amenazas críticas como Ransomware y Fuerza Bruta. Actuamos sobre tu infraestructura para neutralizar ataques antes de que afecten al negocio.</p>
        <span class="svc-tag">24/7 · VRI</span>
      </article>
      <article class="svc-card fade-in">
